Tk::Xcursor
===========

Access Xcursor library from Perl/Tk. This will only work on modern X11
systems.

INSTALLATION

With a modern CPAN.pm ($CPAN::VERSION >= 1.88_55) just do:

   cpan .

Or build and install manually by using the following commands:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install
